'''羊搔癢症'''（{{lang-en|Scrapie}}），是一種退化性疾病，發生在[[綿羊|綿羊]]及[[山羊|山羊]]上<ref name="pmid1617202">{{cite journal
|author=Detwiler LA
|title=Scrapie
|journal=Rev. - Off. Int. Epizoot.
|volume=11
|issue=2
|pages=491–537
|year=1992
|pmid=1617202
|doi=
}}</ref>，造成它們的神經系統異常。它跟[[牛海綿狀腦病|牛海綿狀腦病]]與鹿的[[慢性消耗病|慢性消耗病]]相同，都是[[傳染性海綿狀腦病|傳染性海綿狀腦病]]的一種，由異常的{{tsl|en|PRNP|朊毒體蛋白}}所引起<ref name="pmid17560089">{{cite journal
|author=Hunter N
|title=Scrapie: uncertainties, biology and molecular approaches
|journal=Biochim. Biophys. Acta
|volume=1772
|issue=6
|pages=619–28
|year=2007
|pmid=17560089
|doi=10.1016/j.bbadis.2007.04.007
|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0925-4439(07)00106-8
}}</ref>。它在1732年於英國的牧場發現。目前沒有傳染至人體的病例<ref>{{cite web|last=National Scrapie Education Initiative|title=Scrapie Fact Sheet|url=http://www.eradicatescrapie.org/About%20Scrapie/Fact%20Sheet.html|publisher=National Institute for Animal Agriculture|accessdate=4 December 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rolf|first=George|title=From Sheep to Humans: Scrapie and Creutzfeldt–Jakob Disease|url=http://www.ecclectica.ca/issues/2002/2/george.asp|publisher=Ecclectica|accessdate=4 December 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827011951/http://www.ecclectica.ca/issues/2002/2/george.asp|archivedate=2011年8月27日}}</ref>。

瘙痒通常影响3至5岁左右的羊。羊出生时和与胎盘组织接触的传播潜力是显而易见的。没有证据显示羊搔癢症能传染给人类<ref name="WikiVet">[http://en.wikivet.net/Scrapie Scrapie] reviewed and published by [[WikiVet|WikiVet]], accessed 12 October 2011.</ref>。

羊搔癢症的名稱來自於它在診斷上特別的病徵，受到感染的羊，會不停的摩擦石頭、樹或籬笆來抓癢<ref name="pmid11258721">{{cite journal
|vauthors=Foster JD, Parnham D, Chong A, Goldmann W, Hunter N |title=Clinical signs, histopathology and genetics of experimental transmission of BSE and natural scrapie to sheep and goats
|journal=Vet. Rec.
|volume=148
|issue=6
|pages=165–71
|year=2001
|pmid=11258721
|doi=10.1136/vr.148.6.165
}}</ref>。

